abstract:

Python has some great graphics packages! in this talk, I'll introduce the fundamentals of 3D graphics and demonstrate how to load 3D models, created in Blender3D, into an OpenGL window using Pyglet and the Ratcave extension.
---
full_description:

Python has some great graphics packages! in this talk, I'll introduce the fundamentals of 3D graphics and demonstrate how to load 3D models, created in Blender3D, into an OpenGL window using Pyglet and the Ratcave extension.
